description: This file defines data models for 'Note' and 'Category' used in a note-taking app. It includes class definitions, data serialization/deserialization methods, and some static data for categories.

classes.name: Note
classes.description: Represents a note with properties like id, title, content, category, createdAt, and updatedAt, including methods for serialization and copying.

classes.name: Category
classes.description: Represents a note category with a name and a static list of default categories.

methods.name: Note.fromMap
methods.description: Creates a Note instance from a map, typically from JSON or database query.

methods.name: Note.toMap
methods.description: Converts a Note instance into a map for storage or transmission.

methods.name: Note.copyWith
methods.description: Creates a copy of this Note with optional new values for properties.
